”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen to the latest book reviews from The Bookwyrms, a community of booklovers. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing" to open the skill. You can say "Alexa, stop" to close the skill. Go to The Bookwyrms website (thebookwyrms.com) to learn more.

Your requests to this skill are not shared with The Bookwyrms.

Happy reading!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
